- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses neural networks and discusses their ability to handle nonlinear non-convex systems. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses control of autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions obstacle point data and collision avoidance.
